| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5061 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d71ff71d-f698-58c4-95c8-51e8cb63c8ce"
